NOTICE ON QUOTED MATERIAL

Course Notes in resources/course-notes/ reproduce excerpts from U.S. federal
regulations and public regulatory guidance. Federal regulations are edicts of
government and carry no copyright; they are reproduced freely and are not
covered by the license above, which applies to the original course content.
Where a source may not be reproduced — a paid consensus standard, for example —
the Note characterizes and cites it rather than excerpting it.
